OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,FThe award-winning drama It's A Sin is
OL,7,Fset to be reimagined as an "immersive"
OL,8,Fdance performance, featuring music
OL,9,Ffrom the Pet Shop Boys.
OL,11,FThe original Channel 4 series, created
OL,12,Fby Russell T Davies in 2021, won
OL,13,Fseveral major awards as it followed a
OL,14,Fgroup of young gay men living through
OL,15,Fthe Aids crisis in 1980s London.
OL,17,FNow, Davies is teaming up with 80s pop
OL,18,Flegends Neil Tennant and Chris Lowe to
OL,19,Fbring the story to the stage at Aviva
OL,20,FStudios in Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
