OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,FDavies, who is also known for reviving
OL,7,FDoctor Who and Queer As Folk, said:
OL,8,F"It's A Sin was such a special show
OL,9,Ffor me, and it's one of the greatest
OL,10,Fhonours of my life to have the show
OL,11,Ftransformed by Rambert into something
OL,12,Fnew and exciting."
OL,14,FPet Shop Boys members Neil Tennant and
OL,15,FChris Lowe said: "The original TV
OL,16,Fdrama was a landmark series which
OL,17,Fcompellingly presented the reality and
OL,18,Ftragedy of the Aids crisis to a mass
OL,19,Faudience."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@RO]wD@ROU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
