OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,FSpeaking about their chart-topping
OL,7,Fsingle It's A Sin, which the show was
OL,8,Fnamed after, they said: "Our song was
OL,9,Fcontemporary with the crisis and we
OL,10,Fare proud to be involved as this
OL,11,Fpoignant and important story is
OL,12,Finterpreted in a different medium."
OL,14,FThe critically acclaimed series
OL,15,Fstarred Olly Alexander and Callum
OL,16,FScott Howells, and also featured
OL,17,FStephen Fry, Tracy-Ann Oberman and US
OL,18,Factor Neil Patrick Harris.
OL,26,@pD@YOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
