FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,FDavies and Pet Shop Boys will produce
OL,7,Fthe stage show which will premiere at
OL,8,FAviva Studios, with a date yet to be
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe production will combine
OL,12,Fcontemporary dance and cinematic
OL,13,Fvisuals to tell an immersive story,
OL,14,Fwith set and video design by Luke
OL,15,FHalls Studio.
OL,17,FThe musicians will also work closely
OL,18,Fwith American singer Roman GianArthur,
OL,19,Fwho will compose the music for the
OL,20,Fshow.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,FIt will be choreographed and directed
OL,7,Fby Rambert's artistic director Benoit
OL,8,FSwan Pouffer, who will also co-write
OL,9,Fthe script with dramaturg Katie
OL,10,FO'Reilly.
OL,12,FPouffer said: "Storytelling sits at
OL,13,Fthe heart of Rambert's mission. This
OL,14,Fis a story we feel compelled to tell
OL,15,Fright now, and collaborating with
OL,16,FRussell ` one of the most powerful
OL,17,Fstorytellers of our time ` is
OL,18,Fincredibly exciting.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,F"Together we're exploring how dance
OL,7,Fand choreography can carry urgent,
OL,8,Femotional narratives in a visceral
OL,9,Fway. I can't wait to share this with
OL,10,Faudiences, and there is so much more
OL,11,Fstill to come as the work evolves."
OL,13,FJohn McGrath, Factory International
OL,14,Fartistic director and chief executive,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We are delighted to be
OL,16,Fpartnering with Rambert on this
OL,17,Fthrilling new project.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
