OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773918340
OL,3,CAward-winning drama It's A Sin to be
OL,4,Cadapted into dance production
OL,6,F"Russell T Davies is an icon, and the
OL,7,Fstory he tells in It's A Sin has
OL,8,Fresonated with all ages. Rambert will
OL,9,Fno doubt re-tell the story with great
OL,10,Fvision and beauty.
OL,12,F"We can't wait to premier this
OL,13,Fcollaboration at our home, Aviva
OL,14,FStudios, before sharing it with an
OL,15,Fexceptional group of national and
OL,16,Finternational co-producers."
OL,18,FFurther details about the production
OL,19,Fare yet to be announced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@\O]
